tor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[9] "Product Information. Kalydeco (ivacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[10] "Product Information. Orkambi (ivacaftor-lumacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[11] "Product Information. Symdeko 4-Week (ivacaftor-tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[12] "Product Information. Norvir (ritonavir)." Abbott Pharmaceutical, Abbott Park, IL.', 1767365206);
